WEBVTT

00:01.389 --> 00:02.854
<i>Previously on</i> Camelot...

00:03.386 --> 00:06.316
How it was... between us.
I've never known that before.

00:06.383 --> 00:08.684
But I need you to know...
I love you.

00:08.751 --> 00:12.621
Leontes loves Guinevere
more than life itself.

00:12.689 --> 00:16.734
A wedge between Arthur and his
champion could bring it all down.

00:16.802 --> 00:20.370
- You keep yourself too alone.
- Why does it bother you?

00:20.437 --> 00:22.869
Because sometimes
I see glimpses

00:22.937 --> 00:25.639
of the man you might be.

00:25.707 --> 00:29.180
She covets Arthur's throne.
Where are you?

00:29.248 --> 00:32.015
Tell me what I have to do.

00:32.083 --> 00:37.450
You said I'd been given the gift
for a reason. Now I know what it is.

00:37.517 --> 00:39.183
Do you really think

00:39.251 --> 00:41.318
that the king will not wonder
where I am?

00:41.386 --> 00:44.990
I know he won't.

00:45.057 --> 00:49.026
- It's good to be home.
- Yes. It is.

00:50.964 --> 00:54.066
♪

